O . I . increases share buyback program . O . I . Corp said on Thursday its board authorized the repurchase of up to a further 400 , 000 shares of common stock , boosting a previous buyback authorization . In December , the company said its board had authorized the repurchase of 400 , 000 shares . Purchases would be made from time to time in the open market , or via private transactions at prices the company considered attractive , O . I . said . Repurchased shares would replace stock issued in acquisitions , the company said . O . I . develops , makes and markets instruments used to prepare , detect , measure , analyze and monitor chemical compounds . ( ( New York newsdesk 212 - 859 - 1610 ) ) 
